               its titles.
               
               You must supply two arguments for <MenuCheck>.  The
               first argument is the title of the menu.  The second
               argument is either Check or UnCheck.

               --------------------------------------------------------------

    Example:   "Menu 'Windows,Use Snapshot' Check"
               "Menu 'Show,Sort on,Name' UnCheck"

               --------------------------------------------------------------

