@node  "UseFilter"  "MegaD 3.1 ARexx Commands Copyright © 1993 John L. Jones"

    Command:   UseFilter

      Usage:   UseFilter [Dest]

Description:   This will use the filters created by AddFilter.
               
               An optional argument, <Dest>, can be supplied.
               If this argument is supplied.  The filter will
               be attached to all "Dest"ination windows only.
               
               If the "Dest" argument is not supplied.  The
               filters will become global to all windows
               (source and "Dest"ination).

    Example:   -

   Built-In:   -

   See Also:   @{" AddFilter   " link "AddFilter"}
               @{" FreeFilter  " link "FreeFilter"}
               @{" FiltersPlus " link "FiltersPlus"}


